are you giving out the right port and IP?

That is sometimes a big problem, but when you are ABSOLUTELY sure that you have the right port and IP, then your at a stop.

I had the same exact problem.

If you want to fix this, you have to be on the System Administrator Account otherwise it won’t work.

And get JDK6u2. That will help too.
